quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth quakes with a violent quaking destined for it
  99,2,And the earth yields up its burdens
  99,3,"And human cries out, \"What is the matter with it?\" –"
  99,4,On that day she will recount all its tidings
  99,5,As your Lord has inspired her to do so
  99,6,"On that day all humans will come forth in different companies, to be shown their deeds (that they did in the world)"
  99,7,"And so, whoever does an atom’s weight of good will see it"
  99,8,And whoever does an atom’s weight of evil will see it